{
  "stem": "3855.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "They couldn't get their feet into the shoes anymore that we were issued because they had swollen up from the cold.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "It was the wrong thing-- the worst thing to do to try to escape the daily routine.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "The marching actually kept you healthy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "I'll be honest with you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "And the reduced calories that you got, it didn't seem to do you any harm.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "Think of it that way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "My bunk-- my commander was a German socialist, a huge fellow, a young fellow, a magnificent chap.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "He tried to protect us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "He warned us of inspections.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "He tried to protect us in the best way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "It's interesting how the good in some humans comes through if it's there, no matter what.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 92,
      "text": "And if the bad is there, it cannot be suppressed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 93,
      "text": "And the days went by like this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 94,
      "text": "I know one day-- we were permitted to get money from home, believe it or not.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 95,
      "text": "There was a-- we were-- we were not permitted to get any goods from home, but money, yes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 96,
      "text": "And there was a general store.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 97,
      "text": "And I bought myself sardines every day as a supplement to my food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 98,
      "text": "I don't know where my parents got the money for me because things were getting very rough.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 99,
      "text": "But my mother managed to send me that little bit of money every two weeks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 100,
      "text": "And I bought myself a can of sardines whenever I could.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 101,
      "text": "And it stuck with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 102,
      "text": "To this day, I eat sardines.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 103,
      "text": "Although now they are without salt or any water.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 104,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But somehow, I [LAUGHS] caught on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were called into a huge room, we were sat down, and dictated what to send home.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My dear blank, blank.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I am well.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I feel fine-- platitudes like this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's-- went to my parents.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
